page.title: Arsenal coach Arsene Wenger says feud with Man U of #39;no interest <b>...</b>
page.text: Arsenal manager Arsene Wenger is tired of talking about his team #39;s 2-0 loss to Manchester United more than a week ago. United ended Arsenal #39;s unbeaten league record of 49 games in a contentious game at Old Trafford on Oct. 24.
